    "## 1. Why Readability Matters\n",
    "\n",
    "### The Importance of Readable Code\n",
    "\n",
    "**Code is read more often than it is written.**\n",
    "- ✅ You will spend ~70% of your time reading code\n",
    "- ✅ Teammates need to understand your code quickly\n",
    "- ✅ Future you will thank present you for clear code\n",
    "- ✅ Readable code reduces bugs and maintenance time\n",
    "- ✅ Clean code is professional code\n",
    "\n",
    "### What Makes Code Readable?\n",
    "1. **Descriptive Names**: Variables that explain their purpose\n",
    "2. **Consistent Style**: Following conventions throughout\n",
    "3. **Appropriate Comments**: Explaining why, not what\n",
    "4. **Clear Structure**: Logical organization and flow\n",
    "5. **Self-Documenting Code**: Code that explains itself\n",
    "\n",
    "### Professional Impact:\n",
    "- **Code Reviews**: Faster, more effective reviews\n",
    "- **Onboarding**: New team members understand code quicker\n",
    "- **Debugging**: Easier to spot issues in clear code\n",
    "- **Maintenance**: Updates and fixes take less time\n",
    "- **Collaboration**: Team members can extend code safely"
   ]
  },
